*.swo

# Project specific

# Track .claude/agents/ and .claude/skills/ at any depth (Claude Code auto-discovery).
# Keep local-machine settings, launch files, and start scripts ignored.
**/.claude/*
!**/.claude/agents/
!**/.claude/agents/**
!**/.claude/skills/
!**/.claude/skills/**
!**/.claude/memory/
!**/.claude/memory/**
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/launch.json
**/.claude/start-vite.*

# Track .codex/config.toml for portable model/reasoning settings;
# keep auth, sessions, and local-only files out.
**/.codex/*
!**/.codex/config.toml
**/.codex/*.local.json
**/.codex/sessions/

wellfi-app/node_modules/
wellfi-app/dist/
wellfi-app/.env
nul

